1
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:34,240
Oh, right...

2
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:40,500
The full moon turns you minks into
those so-called Sulong berserkers.

3
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:54,720
Jack!

4
00:02:00,930 --> 00:02:03,980
You've gone too far, you damn samurai!

5
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:09,110
That you even made it here... That's on us!

6
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:14,910
But you'll never get this close to Kaido again!

7
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:20,370
You-gara stay back!

8
00:02:21,290 --> 00:02:27,500
Jack became our sworn enemy the moment
he ravaged our thousand-year-old dukedom.

9
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:31,340
We told him countless times
the samurai wasn't there...

10
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:35,300
I am that warrior they
claimed was not there, Jack!

11
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,930
It was you...!

12
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,060
I owe them my life!

13
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:43,890
I will repay them a hundred
times over in this battle!

14
00:02:57,660 --> 00:02:59,410
Wait, Master...

15
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:01,580
Please save your strength for Kaido.

16
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:03,330
You too, Your Grace!

17
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:20,220
Very well, I leave them to you.

18
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,220
Thank you.

19
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:26,940
In that case, we'll use every bit of
our strength to take down Kaido!

20
00:04:36,090 --> 00:04:37,590
Stand your ground!

21
00:04:37,590 --> 00:04:39,800
Sulong doesn't last long!

22
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,470
Bring it on!

23
00:04:41,470 --> 00:04:43,430
We're beasts, too!

24
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:09,460
They've started.

25
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:13,540
That blowhard Jack went up there with them?

26
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:16,590
Unlike you, he knows how to read the room.

27
00:05:16,590 --> 00:05:18,170
Huh?!

28
00:05:18,170 --> 00:05:23,640
King... You and I aren't gonna
have a problem here...

29
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,720
are we?!

30
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,600
Shinobu?!

31
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:31,190
Ripe-Ripe Enticement Arts!

32
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:40,860
Quietly...

33
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:53,790
Oh no!

34
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,050
Shinobu!

35
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:04,590
That was a pretty good plan.

36
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:05,970
However...

37
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:07,850
its execution was poor!

38
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:23,320
Shinobu!

39
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,410
Shinobu!

40
00:06:32,910 --> 00:06:36,000
Shinobu!

41
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,340
Lord Momonosuke!

42
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:43,550
How shameful to have been
rendered unconscious!

43
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:44,800
Let us try again!

44
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,560
What the...?!

45
00:06:58,190 --> 00:07:00,570
What?! He's floating!

46
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:02,490
Flying even!

47
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:09,990
Too high!

48
00:07:09,990 --> 00:07:12,450
This is terrifying!

49
00:07:15,410 --> 00:07:17,120
Lord Momonosuke!

50
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,670
What is causing this?!

51
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:26,550
On behalf of Kaido,

52
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:28,220
I'll see to your execution!

53
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:48,200
What's that?!

54
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,410
For real, what is that?

55
00:08:00,670 --> 00:08:02,380
Sangoro!

56
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,750
Sanji?!

57
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:05,630
Sanji!

58
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:06,920
You rock!

59
00:08:10,930 --> 00:08:16,310
Hand over the brat! He must be
erased from this world!

60
00:08:34,830 --> 00:08:36,290
Lord Momonosuke!

61
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:43,380
Hey, Momo!

62
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:46,670
When you shouted out your name...

63
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:47,880
it gave me the chills!

64
00:08:49,130 --> 00:08:50,590
Sangoro...!

65
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:53,220
One day, I will become...

66
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:59,980
the shogun of Wano!

67
00:09:02,610 --> 00:09:04,150
Sangoro!

68
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:09,280
Shinobu, look after Momo!

69
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,610
I shall!

70
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,780
Thank you, Sangoro!

71
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:15,790
Lord Momonosuke!

72
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:17,660
Thank goodness you're okay!

73
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:20,540
The Kozuki must be extinguished!

74
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:22,370
Acceleration Device!

75
00:09:36,850 --> 00:09:37,890
Stealth: Activate!

76
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:57,870
Shooting Star Soba Kick!

77
00:10:57,470 --> 00:10:59,890
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

78
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:02,180
No good...!

79
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:03,600
I'm in trouble...!

80
00:11:07,690 --> 00:11:09,690
Cut it out, bird brain!

81
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:14,900
At this rate, I'll wind up dead
with a hole in my stomach!

82
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:18,200
Just a hole?! I intend to break you in half!

83
00:11:18,910 --> 00:11:21,370
Where's your little vanishing act?!

84
00:11:22,540 --> 00:11:25,210
It's only optical camouflage...

85
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,830
Just let go of me!

86
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:29,290
This is it!

87
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:36,220
Sanji!

88
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:45,770
That attack was crazy...

89
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:48,310
Yamabro! Take care of Momo!

90
00:11:48,310 --> 00:11:50,190
Help Shinobu protect him!

91
00:11:50,190 --> 00:11:51,360
What?! Are you sure?!

92
00:11:51,730 --> 00:11:53,480
Of course I'm sure!

93
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:56,450
Right! That actually makes sense...

94
00:11:56,450 --> 00:11:58,910
b-because he's my son!

95
00:12:01,330 --> 00:12:02,700
Just go!

96
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:04,750
Yeah, leave it to me!

97
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:07,960
A father must look after his son!

98
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,580
Hey, don't ignore me!

99
00:12:09,580 --> 00:12:11,420
Wait for me, Momonosuke!

100
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:14,460
Your father is on his way!

101
00:12:12,170 --> 00:12:14,460
Wait! Tarry here, I say!

102
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:17,050
I won't let you get away!

103
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:23,890
All you louts!

104
00:12:23,890 --> 00:12:28,480
Let's kill every last samurai raiding this place...

105
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,980
and start the banquet over!

106
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:36,860
As for you!

107
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:41,870
The wedding! The tea party!
Even this banquet...!

108
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:46,160
It takes a special kind of someone
to always ruin other people's fun!

109
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:51,750
I'll kill you in a way that
more than pays for your meddling!

110
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:56,510
You'll die a miserable death!

111
00:12:59,050 --> 00:13:01,510
Hegemony!

112
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,050
Crap!

113
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:24,200
Are you trying to kill me?!

114
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:36,130
What is that hag, a monster?!

115
00:13:36,130 --> 00:13:42,470
I heard she's a pirate captain from overseas
with as much infamy to her name as Kaido!

116
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:47,600
What?! Does that mean we're
basically facing two Kaidos?!

117
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:56,320
I wanna go help Momo and Sanji,
but she'll just follow me right to them!

118
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,820
Damn you, Straw Hat...!

119
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,200
I'm surprised you were able to dodge that!

120
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,740
Come, Zeus!

121
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:11,910
Zeus, what's the hold up?!

122
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,040
Why, you little...!

123
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:14,880
She saw us!

124
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:17,710
No, no, no, no, no, no, it's impossible!

125
00:14:17,710 --> 00:14:20,050
Nami! She'll kill us!

126
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:22,220
Bad boy!

127
00:14:24,090 --> 00:14:27,430
Come back here!

128
00:14:27,430 --> 00:14:30,020
O-Okay, Mama...

129
00:14:30,020 --> 00:14:31,350
Zeus!

130
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:33,230
Me or Big Mom!

131
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:34,900
Who do you choose?!

132
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:38,110
I can't disobey Mama!

133
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:40,780
Enough already!

134
00:14:46,370 --> 00:14:49,580
Naaamiii!

135
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:53,370
You damn Cat Burglar!

136
00:14:57,420 --> 00:15:00,050
This is all my fault...!

137
00:15:00,050 --> 00:15:01,920
Sorry, Mama.

138
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:07,220
I promise not to wander off anymore,
so please forgive me!

139
00:15:07,220 --> 00:15:10,640
Oh, so now you're back on my side?

140
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:18,610
How can I trust someone who would
follow an annoying tramp like her?!

141
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:22,320
What should I do?!

142
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:25,240
How can I earn back your trust?!

143
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:27,740
You know what to do.

144
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:31,370
I need you to kill that bitch.

145
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:35,960
The watch?

146
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:38,710
♪ Threw it away! ♪

147
00:15:38,710 --> 00:15:41,630
♪ I'm the wind, baby! ♪

148
00:15:44,090 --> 00:15:47,220
You already know, right, Zeus?!

149
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:49,640
If you hold back, you're history!

150
00:15:51,310 --> 00:15:52,600
No!

151
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:55,350
Soul Sensor: Activate!

152
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:02,110
I'm sorry, Nami!

153
00:16:02,110 --> 00:16:04,740
Rest in peace!

154
00:16:04,740 --> 00:16:07,070
I hate you!

155
00:16:07,070 --> 00:16:09,110
We are so through!

156
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:15,120
Someone help me!

157
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,290
Wings?

158
00:16:16,290 --> 00:16:18,460
♪ I will spread them wide! ♪

159
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:20,330
♪ 'Cause I am a bird! ♪

160
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:26,260
– ♪ Flutter my wings and fly away! ♪
– ♪ Flutter my wings and fly away! ♪

161
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:32,140
– ♪ High in the sky and on the wind! ♪
– ♪ High in the sky and on the wind! ♪

162
00:16:33,430 --> 00:16:40,270
♪ I'm Free Rider Franky! ♪

163
00:16:53,660 --> 00:16:55,450
There. You've been cut!

164
00:16:57,330 --> 00:16:59,000
– What?!
– What?!

165
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:01,040
Huh?

166
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:10,260
Oops! I think I ran over something!

167
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,060
Oh well!

168
00:17:15,850 --> 00:17:18,180
As long as it wasn't a flower.

169
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:23,650
Big Bro!

170
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:27,730
Mama...!

171
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:29,030
Mama!

172
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:31,530
Now they've done it!

173
00:17:31,530 --> 00:17:34,160
They're dead men!

174
00:17:36,490 --> 00:17:40,210
He ran over Big Mom with his bike!

175
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:46,420
Big Bro!

176
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:51,380
Thank you, Franky!

177
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,050
Nami!

178
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,760
Are you okay?!

179
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:56,640
Oh, yeah! I'm fabulous!

180
00:17:57,180 --> 00:17:59,560
With Big Bro here, we're all set!

181
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:03,060
Go! Samurai warriors!

182
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:11,320
Looks like it's started.

183
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,740
Well, well...

184
00:18:13,740 --> 00:18:16,120
Look who they ran over.

185
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:18,870
Care to partake, Nico Robin?

186
00:18:18,870 --> 00:18:21,000
Why, I'd be delighted.

187
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,040
Nice!

188
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:26,250
Franky and Brook came through as always!

189
00:18:26,250 --> 00:18:28,590
In that case...

190
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:31,170
I'll help Kin'emon!

191
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:32,630
Here I go!

192
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:38,600
There you are!

193
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,230
You're okay!

194
00:18:42,230 --> 00:18:44,350
Kozuki Momonosuke!

195
00:18:47,190 --> 00:18:48,150
Who are you?!

196
00:18:55,660 --> 00:18:57,410
Hey, Shinobu!

197
00:18:58,660 --> 00:19:00,790
He's our ally!

198
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:02,290
You can trust him!

199
00:19:02,290 --> 00:19:04,580
What? Our ally?!

200
00:19:07,540 --> 00:19:10,590
It's safer to be with him
than to be by yourselves.

201
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:14,260
See ya!

202
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:19,850
Are you truly an ally?

203
00:19:19,850 --> 00:19:21,060
Yeah!

204
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:26,310
Very well.

205
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,520
I will trust you.

206
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:29,400
Please tell us your name!

207
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:32,110
– What?!
– What?!

208
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:34,440
I am...

209
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:42,200
I am Kozuki Oden!

210
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:46,830
I shall protect you!

211
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:51,500
Father...

212
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:54,380
Lord Oden...

213
00:20:01,010 --> 00:20:03,220
Fath... er?

214
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,060
Breasts...

215
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:06,940
Horns...!

216
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:09,860
You are not my father!

217
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:13,190
You are far too suspicious!
You are certainly our enemy!

218
00:20:13,190 --> 00:20:14,320
What?!

219
00:20:16,490 --> 00:20:18,280
Smoke Escape Technique!

220
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,320
Wait!

221
00:20:20,120 --> 00:20:22,120
Why are you running away?!

222
00:20:34,670 --> 00:20:36,340
We're heavily outnumbered.

223
00:20:36,340 --> 00:20:38,180
This will take forever.

224
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:39,840
You're right!

225
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:44,010
Fighting these underlings is a waste of time!

226
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:48,520
The dinosaurs of the Soaring Six
that Denjiro mentioned...

227
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,900
Should we go take their heads?

228
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:53,360
We might be a little outclassed...

229
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:57,780
but we can at least stall them!

230
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:04,410
Really now, I didn't see that coming...

231
00:21:04,410 --> 00:21:06,580
Big Mom's gonna go berserk!

232
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:08,580
Run for it!

233
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:25,600
You're popping up one after another...

234
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:29,730
Straw Hats!

235
00:21:33,150 --> 00:21:36,610
Soul King. How nice to see you again.

236
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:42,570
I see your little group is made up
of some truly rare creatures!

237
00:21:44,450 --> 00:21:45,910
You have good taste!

238
00:21:46,910 --> 00:21:50,790
You like my iron body, you old hag?

239
00:21:51,710 --> 00:21:53,710
My name is...

240
00:21:57,710 --> 00:21:59,630
Franky!

241
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,220
A bona fide cyborg!

242
00:22:06,100 --> 00:22:08,430
I'm not just rare, but strong, too!

243
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:10,600
Cut it out, guys!

244
00:22:11,060 --> 00:22:13,230
We need to run! She's an Emperor!

245
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:15,730
An Emperor...?

246
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:19,030
We run from those?

247
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:22,780
Hey, Nami.

248
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:23,910
Don't you want...

249
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:26,780
to make our captain...

250
00:22:29,540 --> 00:22:34,670
the King of the Pirates?!

251
00:22:43,380 --> 00:22:45,800
Franky...

252
00:22:46,930 --> 00:22:49,560
Radical...

253
00:22:49,560 --> 00:22:50,680
Bea–

254
00:22:53,560 --> 00:22:54,730
Wha...?!

255
00:22:54,730 --> 00:22:57,440
What kind of giant monstrosities...?!

256
00:23:01,650 --> 00:23:02,990
Hey!

257
00:23:02,990 --> 00:23:06,200
You were assigned to a different banquet hall!

258
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:09,410
Numbers!

259
00:23:15,620 --> 00:23:17,500
No!

260
00:23:17,500 --> 00:23:19,670
They're as big as Oars!

261
00:23:19,670 --> 00:23:21,130
What are they?!

262
00:23:23,050 --> 00:23:25,510
It's like Thriller Bark all over again...!

263
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:35,020
Are these the guys Kaido
bought from Punk Hazard?!

264
00:23:35,020 --> 00:23:38,100
The failed recreations of the ancient giants?!

265
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:41,320
How lovely...!

266
00:23:43,610 --> 00:23:46,070
In that monster's hand...!

267
00:23:46,780 --> 00:23:48,620
The Brachio Tank!

268
00:23:48,620 --> 00:23:50,370
Wasn't Usopp's team in there?!

269
00:23:50,370 --> 00:23:56,290
Hands off the hardware, you overgrown mole!

270
00:23:58,540 --> 00:24:00,420
Franky...

271
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:05,130
Radical...

272
00:24:07,090 --> 00:24:09,430
Beam!

273
00:24:24,530 --> 00:24:27,280
My laser beam...

274
00:24:27,280 --> 00:24:29,070
is unstoppable now!

275
00:24:30,570 --> 00:24:33,660
Are you sure you didn't want
to shoot it this way...

276
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:36,790
Iron Man?

277
00:24:41,790 --> 00:24:43,500
Your arm, if I may!

278
00:24:44,340 --> 00:24:46,670
Fishman Jujutsu...

279
00:24:47,130 --> 00:24:48,510
Mil Fleurs...

280
00:24:54,060 --> 00:24:59,440
...Whirlpool Shoulder Throw!

281
00:25:03,770 --> 00:25:05,400
...Delphinium!

282
00:25:07,940 --> 00:25:10,910
Damn you, Jinbe!

283
00:25:10,910 --> 00:25:13,030
I remember what you did to my fleet!

284
00:25:13,490 --> 00:25:16,910
I'll kill you, too!

285
00:25:20,790 --> 00:25:22,920
You're welcome to try!

286
00:25:29,380 --> 00:25:30,550
How was that?

287
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:35,810
Even better than I expected!

288
00:25:35,810 --> 00:25:38,270
She'll return angrier than ever!

289
00:25:40,520 --> 00:25:43,310
You certainly are a remarkable woman!

290
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:45,070
My bad!

291
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:48,400
Thanks for the assist, you two!

292
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:51,780
I'm just glad you're unharmed!

293
00:25:52,450 --> 00:25:54,160
Now then...

294
00:25:58,700 --> 00:26:01,210
It's the moment you've all been waiting for.

295
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:13,800
Come in, Commander Chopper!

296
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:17,310
Usopp!

297
00:26:17,310 --> 00:26:19,430
Wake up! Usopp!

298
00:26:20,060 --> 00:26:21,730
We got a call from Franky!

299
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,480
Hey! You guys are okay, right?!

300
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:30,990
The Brachio Tank is the world's greatest...

301
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:34,320
Do you remember the promise?!

302
00:26:35,870 --> 00:26:37,950
The pro... mise...?

303
00:26:38,280 --> 00:26:40,370
A pirate made of iron...

304
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:43,120
the Iron Pirate!

305
00:26:43,120 --> 00:26:45,080
It's docking time!

306
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:46,250
Dock...

307
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:48,460
...ing?

308
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:57,600
– Docking!
– Docking!

309
00:26:59,890 --> 00:27:01,980
Oh, I can see the sky.

310
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:05,100
Okay, I think I can get up from here.

311
00:27:07,150 --> 00:27:08,230
Don't move!

312
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:10,400
Your Awesomeness!

313
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,780
Shut up. I'm on break.

314
00:27:12,780 --> 00:27:13,740
It's Straw Hat!

315
00:27:15,610 --> 00:27:17,200
What?! Straw Hat?!

316
00:27:19,330 --> 00:27:21,120
And he isn't alone?!

317
00:27:21,620 --> 00:27:23,500
Hey, Zoro!

318
00:27:23,500 --> 00:27:25,000
There you are, Luffy!

319
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,330
Where are you headed?

320
00:27:26,330 --> 00:27:28,040
Up to where Kaido is!

321
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,340
I'll come with you.

322
00:27:30,340 --> 00:27:32,210
As if I would just let you by!

323
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:43,390
What's that giant creature down there?!

324
00:27:44,980 --> 00:27:46,020
Alright!

325
00:27:48,650 --> 00:27:51,270
Gum-Gum...

326
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:53,820
Rocket!

327
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:56,610
I can make it!

328
00:27:56,990 --> 00:27:58,450
Kaido's up there?

329
00:27:58,450 --> 00:28:01,950
Yeah! Kin'emon's group is
already up there fighting!

330
00:28:01,950 --> 00:28:03,910
Almost there!

331
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:14,010
Dammit!

332
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:17,340
You bastards are mine, now!

333
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:22,640
This is as far as you go!

334
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:28,770
We'll never get up there like this!

335
00:28:28,770 --> 00:28:31,190
They've got the sky totally blocked off!

336
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:56,970
Here we go-go-go!

337
00:28:56,970 --> 00:28:59,470
Let's do this thing!

338
00:29:01,140 --> 00:29:04,180
– Docking Formation!
– Docking Formation!

339
00:29:12,730 --> 00:29:14,070
Black Rhino: Stand By!

340
00:29:16,530 --> 00:29:19,950
– Brachio Head: Change!
– Brachio Head: Change!

341
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:24,740
Sorry! This robot is a single-seater.

342
00:29:24,740 --> 00:29:26,240
What?!

343
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:28,710
You can't do this!

344
00:29:28,710 --> 00:29:30,370
Those two are...

345
00:29:30,370 --> 00:29:32,790
Usohachi! Chopperemon!

346
00:29:33,210 --> 00:29:34,710
You doing okay?!

347
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:39,720
We can't thank you enough for your
sacrifice back at the pleasure hall!

348
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:42,640
Guys, there are more important
things at hand!

349
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,010
At hand!

350
00:29:44,010 --> 00:29:46,970
Feast your eyes on the wonders of docking!

351
00:29:46,970 --> 00:29:47,850
Feast your eyes!

352
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:05,780
Iron Pirate...

353
00:30:06,530 --> 00:30:09,620
General Franky!

354
00:30:13,830 --> 00:30:15,420
Here I go!

355
00:30:16,540 --> 00:30:18,460
Franky Cannon!

356
00:30:20,260 --> 00:30:22,380
Of course you shot it yourself!

357
00:30:22,380 --> 00:30:23,380
Of course!

358
00:30:29,180 --> 00:30:31,230
Super!

359
00:30:31,230 --> 00:30:33,190
Jaki's down!

360
00:30:33,190 --> 00:30:35,060
Hey, this is real bad!

361
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:37,690
Let's just get away from here!

362
00:30:37,690 --> 00:30:38,820
Good thinking!

363
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,070
Where's Momo?

364
00:30:46,620 --> 00:30:47,740
I guess he got away...

365
00:30:48,410 --> 00:30:50,790
This suit is annoyingly sturdy...

366
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:56,040
Oh, I'm sorry!

367
00:30:56,040 --> 00:30:59,750
This situation kind of tickles my funny bone.

368
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:02,970
We're still surrounded by enemies.

369
00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:06,140
But for some reason,

370
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:08,390
I can't imagine losing.

371
00:31:08,390 --> 00:31:09,640
You're right!

372
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,270
Yeah, me neither!

373
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:14,520
It's strange. Why do we feel this way?

374
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:16,520
It's obvious, isn't it?!

375
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:19,610
It's because Sir Straw Hat is with us!

376
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:25,780
I thought I could get there just by jumping.

377
00:31:25,780 --> 00:31:27,660
Damn. Guess it won't be that easy.

378
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:29,580
I'll come with you.

379
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:32,620
Let's just get to the top!

380
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,710
What a pain...

381
00:31:37,710 --> 00:31:40,710
Can all these bastards fly?

382
00:31:41,130 --> 00:31:44,420
Tear off their wings,
and they're just caterpillars.

383
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:47,550
That's horrific! Your analogies
are always so scary!

384
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:53,560
So these are the Superstars
we've heard so much about.

385
00:31:57,400 --> 00:32:01,860
They may look tough, but they
don't hold a candle to our captain!

386
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,150
Yeah!

387
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:07,610
It's my duty as a navigator to get
the captain to his destination!

388
00:32:11,280 --> 00:32:13,580
Super count on me!

389
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:16,910
Let the General Franky clear the way for you!

390
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:21,540
Let's go, Captain!

391
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:27,260
Yeah! One more time! Ready?!

392
00:32:28,180 --> 00:32:31,350
Everyone! I'll leave the rest to you!

393
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:33,100
Back us up!

394
00:32:48,360 --> 00:32:50,110
I'm gonna go...

395
00:32:51,370 --> 00:32:53,410
kick Kaido's ass!

396
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:05,890
Roddy & BB
Whale Forest Guardians

397
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:05,890
Roddy & BB
Whale Forest Guardians

398
00:04:19,530 --> 00:04:22,990
Giovanni, Shishilian, & Concelot
Inuarashi's Three Musketeers

